35
00:02:13,666 --> 00:02:16,416
The troll gutting itself,
and its entrails spilling out?

36
00:02:19,458 --> 00:02:20,791
Hey, are you okay?

37
00:02:22,166 --> 00:02:23,250
Are you okay?

38
00:02:24,458 --> 00:02:26,791
Relax. I'm fine.

39
00:02:26,875 --> 00:02:27,916
