115
00:09:37,916 --> 00:09:40,833
TINY TROLLY MOLLY

116
00:09:49,916 --> 00:09:50,916
Vemork?

117
00:09:58,541 --> 00:10:03,000
VEMORK POWER STATION
RJUKAN

118
00:10:15,875 --> 00:10:17,375
Professor Sinkhole?

119
