126
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:45,500
But secrets have a tendency
to be exposed sooner or later.

127
00:10:45,583 --> 00:10:46,416
Yes.

128
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,333
Like trolls in the sun.

129
00:10:49,333 --> 00:10:51,333
