around the troll.

146
00:12:42,291 --> 00:12:45,083
Powerful enough
to turn it to stone in an instant.

147
00:12:45,166 --> 00:12:47,583
Inspired by
your creative solution in Oslo.

148
00:12:50,083 --> 00:12:51,791
What are you guys doing?

149
00:12:52,375 --> 00:12:54,000
