173
00:14:05,708 --> 00:14:09,791
Yeah, its DNA has more in common
with a spruce tree than a human.

174
00:14:11,166 --> 00:14:12,291
Well, they are nature.

175
00:14:14,166 --> 00:14:15,083
What was that?

176
00:14:16,166 --> 00:14:17,583
Trolls are nature.

177
00:14:18,833 --> 00:14:20,750
"Made of earth and stone."

178
00:14:20,833 --> 00:14:23,041
"A snow-clad heart and icy bones."

179
00:14:25,041 --> 00:14:26,708
Nursery rhymes and superstition.

180
00:14:30,916 --> 00:14:32,666
Right. Are we done here?

181
00:14:33,625 --> 00:14:37,041
No. You haven't seen everything yet.
You haven't seen...

