- We didn't really have that kind of thing.

188
00:15:05,333 --> 00:15:07,500
But then it became that kind of thing.

189
00:15:07,583 --> 00:15:09,208
Yeah, clearly.

190
00:15:09,291 --> 00:15:12,833
