259
00:23:43,333 --> 00:23:47,291
AIR FORCE BASE
RYGGE

260
00:24:07,541 --> 00:24:08,916
Captain Kris.

261
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:12,416
Nora Tidemann.
Right in the middle of it all, as usual.

262
00:24:13,291 --> 00:24:15,833
